### Get Ranked Products - Example 1: Sales Emphasis
GET http://localhost:8080/products?weights=sales:0.8,stock:0.2
Accept: application/json

### Get Ranked Products - Example 2: Stock Emphasis
GET http://localhost:8080/products?weights=sales:0.2,stock:0.8
Accept: application/json

### Get Ranked Products - Example 3: Only Sales (Stock weight is 0)
GET http://localhost:8080/products?weights=sales:1.0,stock:0.0
Accept: application/json

### Get Ranked Products - Example 4: Invalid Weight Format (Should return 400 Bad Request)
GET http://localhost:8080/products?weights=sales:0.8,stock:invalid
Accept: application/json

### Get Ranked Products - Example 5: Missing Weights Parameter (Should return 400 Bad Request)
GET http://localhost:8080/products
Accept: application/json
